Amendment No. 2 to HB2115
Crawford
Signature of Sponsor
AMEND S e n ate Bill No. 2581 House Bill No. 2115*
by adding the following as a new subsection (g) to the amendatory language of SECTION 1:
(g) As used in this section, "vacant property":
(1) Means parcels of real property zoned for commercial or industrial use; and
(2) Does not include parcels of real property that contain single-family residential
units or multi-family residential units, or any real property within the jurisdiction and
control of the Tennessee housing development agency pursuant to title 13, chapter 23,
part 1.
